{"body": "The amount of a person\u2019s appropriate maximum housing benefit in any week shall be 100 per cent. of his eligible rent calculated on a weekly basis in accordance with regulations 80 and 81 (calculation of weekly amounts and rent free periods) less any deductions in respect of non-dependants which fall to be made under regulation 74 (non-dependant deductions).", "citation_label": "UKSI 2006/213 reg. 70", "citation_path": "uk/regulation/uksi/2006/213/70", "document_class": "regulation", "expression_date": "2026-04-06", "heading": "Regulation 70", "id": "8f489139-c5bf-58d5-9fd1-eb7de3852b73", "identifiers": {"legislation.gov.uk:number": "213", "legislation.gov.uk:provision": "70", "legislation.gov.uk:type": "uksi", "legislation.gov.uk:year": "2006"}, "jurisdiction": "uk", "kind": "regulation", "language": "en", "legal_identifier": "UKSI 2006/213 reg. 70", "level": 1, "metadata": {"extent": ["E", "W", "S"], "references_to": ["uksi/2006/213"], "retrieved_at": null}, "ordinal": 70, "source_as_of": "2026-07-05", "source_document_id": "uksi/2006/213", "source_format": "legislation.gov.uk-clml", "source_id": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2006/213/regulation/70", "source_path": "sources/uk/regulation/2026-07-05-uk-housing-benefit-entitlement/uksi/2006/213/regulation-70.xml", "source_url": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2006/213/regulation/70", "version": "2026-07-05-uk-housing-benefit-entitlement"}
